411
00:42:16,833 --> 00:42:18,384
- There's one for you, too, Noriko.

412
00:42:18,478 --> 00:42:19,811
Thank you.

413
00:42:20,239 --> 00:42:21,345
It's pitch dark.

414
00:42:21,365 --> 00:42:22,471
